$5 {[%csl Ga5][%cal Gd2b3] White prepares Nd2-b3-a5 maneuver, which would
indeed allow him to claim an edge. This is why we have to act immediately:} a5
$1 12. axb5 ({Alternatively} 12. Bb2 Nbd7 13. axb5 cxb5 14. Nb3 axb4 15. cxb4 {
leads to a very symmetrical position, where Black has a direct way to equalize:
} Rxa1 (15... Rc8 {[%cal Gd7b6,Gb6a4]} 16. Na5 Ba8 {is also possible,
preparing Nb6-a4 maneuver.}) 16. Qxa1 d5 $5 {with good counterplay in the
