{[%cal Ge7e5]}) 10... Nxg5 11. Nxg5 Bd7 12. Bxc6 bxc6 {[%cal Gf7f6,Ge7e5]
Black has the bishop pair, though White can keep the position semi-closed with}
13. f4 {This prevents the key f6-e5 break for the time being, though it
