15. Qe2 (15. Qd2 Qc7 $13 {[%cal Ga5c4] preparing ...Na5-c4, while} 16. Ne5+ {
only helps Black secure his king:} Kc8 $15) 15... Qa6 $5 16. Qxa6 bxa6 {
and here doubled pawns are not such a big problem for Black because he has
